content.rendered:
Directed by Behzad Khambata.

Written by Pranav Adarsh. Pradip Atluri. Behzad Khambata.

Cast Sunny Deol(ATS Chief SS Dewan). Karan Kapadia(Hanif). Karanvir Sharma(Rohit). Ishita Dutta(Husna). Rashika Pradhan(Zainab) . Shaji Chaudhary(Terrorist). Komal Chhabria(DGP Aruna Gupta). Hemant Choudhary(Doctor (as Hemant Chaudhary)). Boloram Das(Farooq). Sanjay Gurbaxani(Doctor). Jatin Jaiswal(Rafique). Jameel Khan(Maqsood). Aarav Mishra(Shopkeeper). Ashok Pandey(Father). Yashraj Rawal(Suicide bomber). Kumar Saurabh(Farooq Neighbour). Kishori Shahane(Dewan’ Wife). Rajinder Sharma(ATS). Vivek Tripathi(Sleeper cell). Ashish Tyagi(Ali)

Language Hindi.

Producers Shrikant Bhasi. Tony D’souza. Rahul Gandhi. Shivanshu Pandey. Nishant Pitti. Rajugopal Podala. Vishal Rana.

Production Carnival Motion Pictures. Echelon Productions.
